articles.title: Linda Evangelista had mastectomy after breast cancer diagnosis - BBC
articles.description: The supermodel reveals she has "one foot in the grave" after her cancer returned following surgery.
articles.content:
Linda Evangelista has revealed she was diagnosed with breast cancer in 2018 and underwent a double mastectomy.
